'''2020年摩爾多瓦總統選舉'''於2020年11月1日（星期日）舉行首輪投票。<ref name="voa01">{{Cite web|title=Moldovans Vote for President as Pro-Moscow Incumbent Aims for Second Term|url=https://www.voanews.com/europe/moldovans-vote-president-pro-moscow-incumbent-aims-second-term|accessdate=2020-11-18|date=2020-11-01|publisher=Voice of America - English|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221092750/https://www.voanews.com/europe/moldovans-vote-president-pro-moscow-incumbent-aims-second-term|dead-url=no}}</ref>前總理[[瑪亞·桑杜|瑪亞·桑杜]]在首輪投票領先爭取第二個任期的[[伊戈尔·多东|伊戈尔·多东]]及其他6位候選人，但得票不過半而需要於11月15日舉行次輪投票。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Moldova Holding the Second Round of Presidential Election|url=https://www.voanews.com/europe/moldova-holding-second-round-presidential-election|accessdate=2020-11-18|date=2020-11-15|publisher=Voice of America - English|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207185033/https://www.voanews.com/europe/moldova-holding-second-round-presidential-election|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==選舉制度==
總統選舉採用[[两轮选举制|两轮选举制]]。候選人可以由政黨或選舉聯盟提名，也可以無黨籍身份參選。候選人需收集不少於15,000個選民簽名支持方可參選，簽名需來自全國至少半數二級行政區，每區不少於600個。<ref>{{cite web|title=Regulations|url=http://old.cec.md/files/files/Legi/tabel_regulamente/Regulament%20privind%20modul%20de%20%C3%AEntocmire%2C%20prezentare%20si%20verificare%20a%20listelor%20de%20subscriptie.pdf|accessdate=2020-11-02|date=3 July 2018|format=PDF|work=old.cec.md|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116123016/http://old.cec.md/files/files/Legi/tabel_regulamente/Regulament%20privind%20modul%20de%20%C3%AEntocmire%2C%20prezentare%20si%20verificare%20a%20listelor%20de%20subscriptie.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>投票率需達到33%或以上，投票結果方為有效。

